{"tid":631303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：黑恤男屈人非禮 正義大叔證虛構","createTime":"2018-04-16T10:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T04:57:21.000Z","uid":67500,"like":117,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1476dc8da45ec17432c33d6f9d438dea6cf2f7","tid":631303,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Yy7n8zUUVG1.67HZGPgpXA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/c2ad4f33b1fc07d66b877f942404f37e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FYy7n8zUUVG1.67HZGPgpXA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fc2ad4f33b1fc07d66b877f942404f37e&h=7182dd75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n忍一時風平浪靜，身邊有小朋友卻為了小事嘈交，面臨起底，多無謂呢！多個Facebook群組瘋傳一則巴士上故事，據形容，一對夫婦在巴士上因囡囡敲櫈發出噪音被男乘客望一望，疑為丈夫的黑恤男便與男乘客不咬弦，阻人下車。最令網民起火是黑恤男一度「屈」男乘客非禮其妻，幸有目擊經過的大叔挺身而出，力證有人虛構事件，雖然大叔夾雜粗口，但網民狂給like：「呢啲真係要起底組做嘢，好彩有正義大叔！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據fb貼文描述，正義大叔成功阻止的一宗「明屈事件簿」，發生於昨日(14日)近傍晚時分開往馬鞍山的81C線巴士上。當時，黑恤男的囡囡用物件敲櫈發出噪音，坐在前面的一名青年因此望了小女孩一眼，該對夫婦即指摘青年「兇」小女孩，黑恤男更挑釁青年以拳腳解決事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更甚是當青年欲下車之際，黑恤男即用腳攔住，還指青年非禮其妻而要報警。不過，整個過程也有人目擊，一名大叔更看不過眼便開聲指摘黑恤男「屈人」，黑恤男即面懵懵，無聲出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFatlung Chan：好在有人睇唔過眼，唔係個靚仔硬食！<br />\n<br />\nAda Kam Chiu Chu：自己想小朋友有好品格，唔係背書，係以身作則！<br />\n<br />\nKelly Wong：比(畀)多多掌聲果(嗰)個俠士。<br />\n<br />\nMei Yee：帶住個女都咁賤格，不知所謂，教壞自己個女呀。<br />\n<br />\nChikan Fung：香港真係好多冇品又野蠻既(嘅)人"},{"pid":"965d557e29f3d66e97c4cc76edf441a0510b5032","tid":631303,"uid":10197,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 證明自己有非禮仲難過係青山證明自己係正常人"},{"pid":"5e29deb4420cfbe5449ec659137b36735d7e147b","tid":631303,"uid":10197,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 證明自己<del>有</del>冇非禮仲難過係青山證明自己係正常人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a8604cc407b33494f146ce85457c1ece17d566e9","tid":631303,"uid":113929,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"係咪可以告返個女人？"},{"pid":"c77e281c4216f9ae9bfaa4fdfde7eac8a5d77c74","tid":631303,"uid":67500,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"成撚日打格仔，屌你老味記者扮道德撚"},{"pid":"91578644c662bcd27f2f45297c3a04d0feb048ca","tid":631303,"uid":38456,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:04:56.000Z","msg":"無波點非禮"},{"pid":"76484d2e69d806bc40f056e998bb8cf93dec3e6b","tid":631303,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8604cc407b33494f146ce85457c1ece17d566e9","tid":631303,"uid":113929,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"係咪可以告返個女人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:05:09.000Z","msg":"告告告，告乜撚，直接打柒佢最快"},{"pid":"ef8f51dd3cf4b5a1a19ef794512cd4deec4f0d05","tid":631303,"uid":8410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"有無原圖，起佢2公婆底俾佢地知道俾人欺凌有幾慘"},{"pid":"6a182ab44913e0818a93a87d0f2cca9282bc5242","tid":631303,"uid":56782,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/maonshanhk/permalink/1959881677369782/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fmaonshanhk%2Fpermalink%2F1959881677369782%2F&d=4FvlyEH6dK%2B%2FrrW2fqsZeDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e50ec6a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/maonshanhk/permalink/1959881677369782/</a>"},{"pid":"304a223325b347f2f20e41f3db9b4430154b315b","tid":631303,"uid":56782,"like":121,"dislike":1,"score":120,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:11:40.000Z","ms